            <h3>🐛 The Bug: Read-Modify-Write Race</h3>
            <p>
                Each concurrent task reads the shared <code>progress</code> variable,
                adds its chunk, and writes back. But when multiple tasks run "simultaneously"
                via interleaved <code>setTimeout</code> / <code>Promise</code> callbacks,
                they all read the <em>same stale value</em> before any of them writes back.
            </p>
            <p>
