<h1>⚡ Concurrency Bug: Progress Bar Tracker</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Watch how shared mutable state causes race conditions in async JavaScript</p>

<div class="grid">

  <!-- ═══════════════════ BUGGY PANEL ═══════════════════ -->
