        <li>Each task owns a private <code>taskProgress[id]</code> slot</li>
        <li>Tasks update only their own slot — no conflicts possible</li>
        <li>A pure <code>getTotal()</code> sums all slots on every render</li>
        <li>No task can overwrite another task's data</li>
        <li>Final result is always exactly <code>sum of all weights = 100%</code></li>
        <li>This mirrors patterns like Redux, atomic counters, and CRDT design</li>
